ThreadPuddle changelog

2.000 July 24, 2016
  * added builder to facility more complicated configuration
  * added option of limitless work queue
  * added finish method which blocks until all work is complete without blocking the addition of new work

1.002 July 17, 2016
  * added optional LIFO semantics for work queue

1.001 September 12, 2014
  * merged in changes from jentfoo, switching Deques for Lists
  * improved interrupt handling

1.0   August 13, 2013
  * initial release
